#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.audiotube.appdata.xml:125
msgid ""
"AudioTube can search YouTube Music, list albums and artists, play "
"automatically generated playlists, albums and allows to put your own "
"playlist together. It is adapted to mobile phones and desktop computers."
msgstr ""
"AudioTube può eseguire ricerche su YouTube Music, elencare album e artisti, "
"riprodurre scalette e album generati automaticamente e ti consente di creare "
"la tua scaletta. È adatto ai telefoni cellulari e ai computer desktop."

#~ msgid "YouTube Music App for phones and desktop computers"
#~ msgstr "Applicazione YouTube Music per telefoni e computer desktop"

